    <div class="container">
      <div class="resources-section-header reveal">
        <h2 class="resources-section-title">Advanced</h2>
        <p class="resources-section-desc">Ready for a challenge? These tutorials cover advanced topics and real-world problem-solving techniques for experienced builders.</p>
      </div>

